<div class="content" name="FAX_VERSION" uuid="43cfd54d-206a-4eb9-b24a-23b732e46d5e"><p>The <b>_FAX_VERSION</b> structure is the custom-marshaled
variant of the <b>FAX_VERSION</b> (section <a href="7ef8f9ec-366f-4414-9583-4d8962c00e87" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.22</a>) structure. The <b>_FAX_VERSION</b>
contains the same information about the version of the fax server components as
contained in the <b>FAX_VERSION</b>. The <b>_FAX_VERSION</b> is embedded in the
<b>FAX_ROUTING_EXTENSION_INFO</b> (section <a href="f9f82598-144c-473f-adc2-ed92e748d3a4" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.49</a>) and <b>FAX_DEVICE_PROVIDER_INFO</b>
(section <a href="7abbf16c-90bb-4bf6-83ec-e0068c7cbc36" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.30</a>)
structures.</p><p>This data structure is custom marshaled as follows and uses
